Welcome to a Luxurious Couple's Retreat in the Heart of Friday Harbour. All year round access to Hot Tub. Treat yourself to a relaxing experience only 1hr from Toronto.

**Convenience** One of the few condos with direct walkout to courtyard's Swimming Pool, Hot Tub, Firepit and BBQs.

(Swimming Pool and Hot Tub are currently closed for repairs, we apologize for any inconvenience)

Steps away from Restaurants, Nature Trails, Beach & Boardwalk, Golfing, Live Music Events every Weekend

The space
Clean and Luxurious design throughout.
Spacious open concept living space with high ceilings and lots of natural light.

Beautifully designed cozy Patio Terrace with direct access to Swimming Pool & Hot Tub.

Ground floor condo with a walkout to the courtyard.

Guest access
(Swimming Pool and Hot Tub are currently closed for repairs, we apologize for any inconvenience)

The Beach Club Pool is now Free of charge for all our guests to enjoy. It's a beautiful venue overlooking the lake and marina, with restaurant and bar.
Reservations can be made with the Welcome Centre on the day of your desired visit.

Direct access to the Swimming Pool, All-Year-Round Hot Tub, Firepit Lounging, and Gas BBQs.
(Amenities are seasonal)
